Spontaneous pregnancy in a woman with 45,X/47,XXX mosaicism in both serum and germ cell lines. A case report. This is the first published case report of pregnancy in a women with 45, X/47, XXX mosaicism in both blood and germ cell lines.The patient conceived, and analysis of ovarian tissue confirmed a karyotype of 45, X/47, XXX.Women with a 45, X/47, XXX karyotype in the germ cell line can conceive, as this case demonstrates.